== Ubuntu Ireland IRC Meetings ==

All Ubuntu Ireland IRC Meetings take place in the #ubuntu-ie channel on irc.freenode.net server. 

Our next meeting will take place on Wednesday the 13^th^ of November at 20:30 local time.

 Please refer to <nowiki>[[https://help.ubuntu.com/community/InternetRelayChat|this wiki page]]</nowiki> for details on how to chat IRC. Alternatively you can simply <nowiki>[[http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=#ubuntu-ie|chat in your browser now]]</nowiki>.

 
=== Upcoming Meeting ===

* On Wednesday the 13^th^ of November at 20:30 local time.   
* Details at: <nowiki>[[http://loco.ubuntu.com/meetings/ubuntu-ie/690/detail/ | Winter Team Meeting]]</nowiki>
